以流行病學的觀點提出如何進行研究來蒐集實證數據，以評論此說法
是否正確？（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "237e460ab73e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00433', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-112-aaf759af', 'sub-public-health-specialist-02', NULL, 'essay', '我國十大死因長期以來一直以慢性病為主，高齡化社會的到來更加重
此一趨勢，為降低慢性病對國人健康及醫療支出的衝擊，近年來政府
推出系列慢性病防治計畫，包括糖尿病共同照護網計畫、國家心血管
疾病防治第一期計畫、代謝症候群防治計畫等，請以流行病學的觀點
提出這些計畫執行成效的評估策略。（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "237e460ab73e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00434', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-112-aaf759af', 'sub-public-health-specialist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '反事實推理（counterfactualreasoning）在因果推論中的目的是什麼？', '["確定暴露與結果之間的關係", "模擬在不同暴露情況下的可能結果", "消除因果相關研究中對統計分析的需求", "建立暴露與結果之間的時序性"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "237e460ab73e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "43eeaa357780", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00435', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-112-aaf759af', 'sub-public-health-specialist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '在隨機分派對照試驗（randomizedcontrolledtrial,RCT）中，隨機分配的目的是什麼？', '["確保治療組和對照組能完全匹配", "減少選擇偏差，使潛在的干擾因素在組間平均分布", "增加研究結果在目標族群的外推性", "允許對研究參與者和研究者能進行加盲"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "237e460ab73e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "43eeaa357780", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00436', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-112-aaf759af', 'sub-public-health-specialist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '在一個巢式病例對照研究（nestedcase-controlstudy）中，以下那個陳述是正確的？', '["對照組是從與病例相同來源的人群中選樣", "會依據暴露狀態來選擇病例組", "此研究設計能夠直接估計疾病發生率", "在這種設計中，必須進行病例和對照的配對"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "237e460ab73e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "43eeaa357780", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
